        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 8 at 10:32PM CDT until September 8 at 11:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>SVRAMA

The National Weather Service in Amarillo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Southwestern Lipscomb County in the Panhandle of Texas...
Southeastern Ochiltree County in the Panhandle of Texas...

* Until 1130 PM CDT.

* At 1032 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles north of
Wolf Creek Park, or 11 miles southeast of Perryton, moving
southeast at 10 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and half dollar size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
Hail damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Wolf Creek Park.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
